                        Out Of Office
                    </a>
                </h2>
                <h3 class="subDescription" style="display:none"></h3>
                <p class="ArticleInfo">[09.09.2010]</p>
                <p>Nearly all employees of The Ministry of Trade and Industry were out of the office on the same day recently. On September 7, they visited a total of 59 companies all over Norway – where they learned about everything from burger-flipping and salmon farming to shipbuilding and beer production.</p>
                
                
